  <Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VFED_ZeusCannon"]/description</xpath>
    <value>
      <description>A relic of ancient Sophiamundan technology, the Orbital Cannon is a closely guarded secret of the Whitespring Enclave. This formidable artillery piece has the unique ability to convert vast quantities of electricity into potent energy blasts. With unmatched range, it can pierce the atmosphere to target and obliterate objects in orbit. A testament to lost engineering brilliance, it stands as both a weapon and a symbol of the Whitespring Enclave&apos;s might.\n\nIt has a long charging cycle, after which it will aim at the target and release a devastating energy blast.</description>
    </value>
